description: [``botocore``] This release adds documentation updates for Audit Manager. We provided examples of how to use the Custom_ prefix for the keywordValue attribute. We also provided more details about the DeleteAssessmentReport operation.
[``botocore``] AWS Network Firewall adds support for stateful threat signature AWS managed rule groups.
[``botocore``] This release adds support to query the public key and creation date of EC2 Key Pairs. Additionally, the format (pem or ppk) of a key pair can be specified when creating a new key pair.
[``botocore``] This release enables Braket Hybrid Jobs with Embedded Simulators to have multiple instances.
[``botocore``] This release introduces an API for changing the current agent status of a user in Connect.
